        "class": "bld",
        "text": "We sought him not:",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " he takes a part of the guilt to himself, because it was his duty, as well as theirs, diligently to read the law and word of God, and to see it executed, and their oversight did not excuse his. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "After the due order; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " according to the rules which he appointed. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
