        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_sub_title",
        "text": "Verse 13.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " - This verse purports to say that the Levites had been deficient in their duty in the double sense of not having themselves exclusively undertaken the removal of the ark, and not having executed that removal after the due order. 1 Chronicles 15:13",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "",
        "children": []
